title: Blac Chyna Shows Off “Future” Tattoo On Ciara’s B-Day
text: Blac Chyna Shows Off “Future” Tattoo On Ciara’s B-Day Sunday, 25 October 2015 (8 minutes ago) Vixen Blac Chyna appears to have no chill after showing off a new tattoo possibly in tribute to rumored rapper boyfriend Future on Ciara’s 30th birthday. Chyna unveiled the jaw-dropping ink job via her Instagram page Sunday (October 25) and referenced Future’s “I Thought It Was A Drought” single.
